{"tid":241162,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android O重大變化 : 手機可以更容易獲得OS升級","createTime":"2017-05-13T02:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T11:12:14.000Z","uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"489df4815fd339854e9b705df675e380811bd4be","tid":241162,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2017/05/here-comes-treble-modular-base-for.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fandroid-developers.googleblog.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fhere-comes-treble-modular-base-for.html&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=94ca0a0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2017/05/here-comes-treble-modular-base-for.html</a><br />\n<br />\n貌似Google重寫左android個architecture, 獨立左個vendor implementation出黎, 以後手機廠商可以直接出OS update而唔洗重寫自己個implementation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但都無撚用啦, 而加問題係手機廠無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊機同平價機都有得update既話邊個會買新機"},{"pid":"cb0899b061a4cf1e66053d2a5416880dad97c261","tid":241162,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"咁係廠問題<br />\n自己技窮諗唔到新野吸引人"},{"pid":"71801adc3af28084dec24cbb0e9b9ec3a9fb0511","tid":241162,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係廠問題<br />\n自己技窮諗唔到新野吸引人</blockquote><br />\n睇下三星機海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 20款機唔知有無3部有update"},{"pid":"7602324f81f3270ab19a031cf26c67b251d58320","tid":241162,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re